    "Name": "Blackjack BJ-1RR",
    "Details": "The BJ-1RR is a comprehensive overhaul of the classic Blackjack frame produced by Firefly Foundry for Riley's Rangers. Endo Steel structure freed enough weight to swap the original AC/2s for LB-2X autocannons and upgrade all four Medium Lasers to ER models, while double heat sinks handle the increased thermal load. Four jump jets carry over from the base design, giving this 45-ton skirmisher solid positional flexibility to support its sustained long-range harassment capability.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Extended Torso Twist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.01</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
